<p><strong>3.图片来源网络，如有侵权，请联系主编删除。</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200908/53595c28998149a3bb9d9d9f9e075908.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
➜湖北诗人朱翠荣（清美玉洁）：七绝《涉外步秋有感》
http://www.sohu.com/a/417078204_100115135	29640
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>七绝《涉外步秋有感》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/朱翠荣(武汉)</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200908/3df67810a001482b80891c091e9c030f.png" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">归阁久居春夏误，今收艳景剪秋光。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">流金丰硕闲愁起，不料梧桐叶已黄。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200908/0ebe9e3b1f9b4a5fa696f48df78c4ccd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">才醉荷莲翻绿伞，又摇秋草荻芦惶。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">此生一世何其短，烟火流光露化霜。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>写于2020年9月7日晚</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200908/73f7068169c741689f316843f5423e56.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
